Package org.aavso.tools.vstar.ui.mediator.message

Class Summary
AnalysisTypeChangeMessage This message is intended to be sent to listeners when VStar's analysis type changes (raw data, phase plot, period analysis) to provide new artefacts.
FilteredObservationMessage Instances of this message should be sent when an observation filtering operation has occurred.
MeanSourceSeriesChangeMessage This message is sent when the source series of the current mean series has changed.
MessageBase A base class for Notifier messages.
NewStarMessage A message class containing new star type and GUI component information.
ObservationChangeMessage This message will be sent to Listener implementers registered with a Notifier implementer.
ObservationSelectionMessage This message is sent to denote the selection of a valid observation from a specific source.
PeriodAnalysisSelectionMessage Instances of this message class can be sent when a period analysis chart data-point selection occurs.
PeriodChangeMessage This message should be sent
ProgressInfo This class encodes information about application progress.
ZoomRequestMessage This message should be sent when a zoom (in or out) action is required by some or all listeners.
 

Enum Summary
ObservationChangeType This enumeration specifies possible changes that may take place on one or more observations.
ProgressType This enum represents application progress.
ZoomType The type of zoom.
